# Competency question: "What cryptographic key schemes does GMEOW recognise for
# the keys an agent holds?" Expected: the KeyScheme individuals (OpenPGP, X.509,
# SSH, Nostr). Schemes are values, not key subclasses — extend by adding
# individuals, so this query keeps working as new schemes are added.

PREFIX gmeow: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/gmeow/>

SELECT ?scheme WHERE {
    ?scheme a gmeow:KeyScheme .
}
ORDER BY ?scheme
